.TH "DALMA" "" "October 2017" "NYUAD" "Dalma Manual"
.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
Here you will find a list of all the available topics for help related to \fBDalma\fR and how to call for help
.
.P
This place will contain most of the documentation/recipes needed to get you to work in Dalma or to solve your most common problems or questions\.
.
.P
However, If there is any information that can not be found here please visit the How To\'s section \fIhttps://wikis\.nyu\.edu/pages/viewpage\.action?pageId=69765337\fR
.
.SH "CONTACT US"
Raise a ticket with email \fInyuad\.it\.help@nyu\.edu\fR\. Or, contact us directly with email \fIdalma\.admins@nyu\.edu\fR\. We are sitting in A2\-131 and A2\-132\. Looking forward to see you!
.
.P
For more information on IT service desk, kindly visit this webpage \fIhttp://www\.nyu\.edu/life/information\-technology/help\-and\-service\-status/nyu\-it\-service\-desk\.html\fR
.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Users can request help on any specific topic using the following command:
.
.P
\fBman dalma\-<topic>\fR
.
